<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1905-10-31T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1905-10-31T00:00:00-05:00" n="665" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d665">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Jackson</persName> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Cettinje</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-10-31"><hi rend="italic">October 31,
                                1905</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Presented credentials to-day. Prince requested me to express gratitude to
                            President. Propose leaving Friday for Greece via Italy. Wilson in charge
                            at Athens.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Jackson.</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>